        eingereicht an der  \\ \vspace*{\stretch{0.5}}
        {\DefThesisFaculty}\\ \vspace*{\stretch{0.5}}
        {\DefThesisInstitute} \\ \vspace*{\stretch{0.5}}
        {\DefThesisUniversity}\\ \vspace*{\stretch{5}}
